· tDCS: Only in research setting, paired with working memory training
· CES: Cranial electrostimulation for anxiety reduction
· Photobiomodulation: Near-infrared therapy for mitochondrial function

5.2 Nootropic Stack (Evidence-Based)

```python
evidence_based_nootropics = {
