    "emerging_evidence": [
        "Lion's mane (1g daily, NGF modulation)",
        "Rhodiola rosea (adaptogen for stress)",
        "Noopept (cautious, short cycles)"
    ],
    "avoid": [
        "Unregulated 'smart drugs'",
        "Racetams without medical supervision",
        "Excessive cholinergic stimulation"
    ]
}
```

